======
 M210
======

:author: `Tuomas R채s채nen (tuos)`_ <tuos@codegrove.org>

.. _Tuomas R채s채nen (tuos): http://tuos.codegrove.org/

M210_ is a software project which aims to provide easy-to-use tools for
controlling and using `Pegasus Mobile Notetaker M210`_ in modern Linux
desktop environments.

.. _M210: http://codegrove.org/projects/m210
.. _Pegasus Mobile Notetaker M210: http://www.pegatech.com/?CategoryID=207&ArticleID=268

Requirements
============

- Python 2.6.x
- Python development files
- dbus-python
- PyQt4
